/**
 * Rewrite relative doc links (e.g. `/guide/timeline`) in changelog markdown
 * to full locale-aware URLs (e.g. `https://voyager.nagi.fun/ja/guide/timeline`).
 * zh is the root locale and gets no prefix.
 */
